hadn't washed or even worn yet.

00:09:29.460 --> 00:09:30.970
Damn it...

00:09:32.630 --> 00:09:37.540
Do you know about the one
who attacked Polnareff, Avdol?

00:09:37.540 --> 00:09:38.440
Indeed.

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:40.180
Soul Sacrifice.

00:09:40.690 --> 00:09:45.270
An assassin who claims to be
a Native American medicine man.

00:09:45.820 --> 00:09:48.450
But he's a terrifying Stand user.

00:09:48.450 --> 00:09:50.590
Mafioso, militaries, and politicians

00:09:50.590 --> 00:09:53.040
from all around the world hire him.

00:09:53.040 --> 00:09:57.150
