00:12:08.820 --> 00:12:11.820
Mr. Polnareff, this is room service.

00:12:11.820 --> 00:12:13.220
I've brought your medicine.

00:12:13.500 --> 00:12:15.720
Get away! You'll be killed!

00:12:15.720 --> 00:12:18.970
Huh? Wh-What has happened here?!

00:12:18.970 --> 00:12:22.100
