00:13:15.530 --> 00:13:22.190
Your Stand isn't one that
can fight where you can't see!

00:13:38.320 --> 00:13:41.010
Ebony Devil

00:13:39.070 --> 00:13:41.010
Soul Sacrifice

00:13:45.270 --> 00:13:46.850
Oh, Jojo.

00:13:48.030 --> 00:13:49.400
Did you need something?

00:13:49.740 --> 00:13:50.610
So you are here.

00:13:51.010 --> 00:13:53.830
Listen up. Don't leave this room for a while.

00:13:53.830 --> 00:13:54.550
Huh?

00:13:54.880 --> 00:13:56.580
