00:14:52.210 --> 00:14:55.980
Talk about dense!

00:15:05.900 --> 00:15:07.360
You bastard...

00:15:07.360 --> 00:15:09.230
Give a rest already...

00:15:09.230 --> 00:15:11.190
You little shrimp!

00:15:15.890 --> 00:15:18.190
It's just you two?

00:15:18.190 --> 00:15:19.860
What happened to the girl?

00:15:19.860 --> 00:15:23.510
Well, we went to check on her...

00:15:23.510 --> 00:15:26.340
But she's not a Stand user, so we thought that

00:15:26.340 --> 00:15:29.870
