more danger by bringing her here.

00:15:30.190 --> 00:15:34.250
Good point. So that just leaves Polnareff.

00:15:34.250 --> 00:15:35.880
But man, is he late...

00:15:36.340 --> 00:15:39.380
It's already been way over five minutes.

00:15:41.700 --> 00:15:43.890
Let me go!

00:15:43.890 --> 00:15:45.310
I've caught you.

00:15:45.310 --> 00:15:46.890
I'm going to snap your spear in half.

00:16:04.250 --> 00:16:05.280
All right.

00:16:05.280 --> 00:16:09.200
Damn it... But a-at least I
finally managed to cut the cord...

00:16:09.200 --> 00:16:12.150
