00:17:49.710 --> 00:17:51.760
Die!

00:17:51.760 --> 00:17:56.170
This should take care of my grudge...

00:17:56.170 --> 00:17:59.600
Polnareff!

00:17:59.840 --> 00:18:04.280
You're not the only one who's
been scattering stuff around!

00:18:06.100 --> 00:18:10.160
H-How did you know where
I was on top of the bed...

00:18:10.160 --> 00:18:12.880
so precisely?!

00:18:12.880 --> 00:18:15.340
I broke a mirror!

00:18:15.340 --> 00:18:19.460
So I can see the top of the
bed really well from this angle.

00:18:24.840 --> 00:18:26.420
